{
  "stem": "10644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was, you know-- we were-- after this-- this-- this intelligence action-- action, for a while, it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had some rations-- not enough, always hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In October-- I will not say exactly on the 13th of October or the 14th of October-- we were ordered to come to a big, empty place in this where we lived-- big empty place.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941, October 14-- October 14th or 15th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then just a few Germans were there, you know, and ask us to parade, by families, one family, two families to parade.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am with my wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was also her aunt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were three persons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "33,000 people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And right away, we're divided with the whole family with kids to the left, without kids, depends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it is old people, to the left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Younger people to the right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so 15,000 people were divided right away into one group. 18,000 into other group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, the 15,000, were asked to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The 18 were taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They stayed in one place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next day, gathered and brought to a Tenth Fort.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told you about Seventh Fort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is Tenth Fort, approximately two, three miles from our place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from the moment we arrived, we started to hear [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] shots, screaming, terrible screaming, which is still in my ears, of this 18,000 people as they realized they are being brought here to be killed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [? always, ?] it lasted almost two days to kill these 18 people of Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18,000 People.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a same thing done in Vilna This was the same thing done in-- in-- and on different days-- in-- in-- in Riga.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Riga, it was done on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
